        <div class="hentry ">
    <h2 class="clearfix contentGroup cgMedium"><a href="/news/technology" title="Latest Technology News" class="cgLabel cgTechnology">Technology</a></h2>   

    
        <h1 class="entry-title">Irrigation system can grow crops with salt water</h1>
    
    <div class="articleMeta clearfix">

            <div class="author">By <a href="/search/author/Katie+Scott" title="View all articles by Katie Scott" class="fn">Katie Scott</a></div>
        
        <div class="published"><abbr class="updated " title="Fri, 01 May 2009 14:32:00 +01:00">01 May 09</abbr></div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix">
        
                <div class="imageWrapper">
                    <img alt="Image1" class="multiImg Landscape_1-50_620" data-src620x258="http://cdni.wired.co.uk/620x258/g_j/Irrigation-674281_620x258.jpg" height="258" src="http://cdni.wired.co.uk/620x258/g_j/Irrigation-674281_620x258.jpg" width="620" />
                    
                </div>
                
        <div class="articleSidebar1">
            
            
                    <div class="related linkList2">
                        <h3>Related features</h3>
                        <ul>
                            
