                                    <a href="/news/archive/2009-01/28/drought-resistant-grass-genes" title="Drought-resistant grass genes could spur 21st century crops">Drought-resistant grass genes could spur 21st century crops</a>
                                </li>
                            
                                <li>
                                    <a href="/news/archive/2010-10/11/alaska-exporting-water" title="Alaska to begin exporting water">Alaska to begin exporting water</a>
                                </li>
                            
